563 ff5 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">friends when they lose respect for themselves? Are your </div><div class="t m526 x59 h20 y564 ff5 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">attempts successful? If not, why not? </div><div class="t m3b8 x33 h1f y565 ff1 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">SUMMARY: </div><div class="t m527 x4a h20 y566 ff5 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">The Song of Solomon begins with Shulamith ex-</div><div class="t m382 x33 h20 y567 ff5 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">pressing doubts as to her beauty and acceptability. Uncertainty </div><div class="t m38b x33 h20 y214 ff5 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">and insecurity crave acceptance and reassurance. As we learn </div><div class="t m528 x33 h20 y568 ff5 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">to respect ourselves because of the love of our heavenly Bride-</div><div class="t m462 x33 h20 y569 ff5 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">groom, we are able to relate with empathy toward others. </div><div class="t m3e2 x8b h14 y56a ff1 fs4 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">For the first time in 70 years, the people of the Soviet Division may buy </div><div class="t m529 x8b h14 y56b ff1 fs4 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Adventist literature again. Support our Soviet Adventist family, our </div><div class="t m38a x8b h14 y56c ff1 fs4 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">newest division, December 26. </div><div class="t m52a x33 h14 y56d ff1 fs4 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">40 </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
